00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:34,000
So maybe like an example, like I'm a really strong leader because in my previous job, I had the best J.D.

303
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:36,000
Power ratings for employee satisfaction.

304
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:37,000
Okay.

305
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:43,000
So you are actually showing with numbers or with facts that you are a great leader.

306
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:48,000
So the key thing here, I think, is identify what your strengths and skills are.

307
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,000
Think of specific examples.

308
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:58,000
If you can, give numbers and show how you can bring this skill and your experiences to the new company.

